## LEARN

![](img/Bear_Logo.png)
  
---

### Project Flexibility
* Projects are constantly moving
* Each meeting with a client or boss may clarify the requirements
* We need a process for adjusting to change


### Technical Debt
* Write yourself an IOU 
* Save the work for later
* Calculate the current debt level


### Best Practices in Software Engineering
* [My Book on Engineering](https://shrinking-world.com/Leverage/)


### Software Process
* Efficient path to release
* Addresses all outstanding debt


### Issue Tracking
* Test - Capture all outstanding issues
* Fix - Pay off existing debt
* Closure - Resolve the disagreements


### Teamwork
* Work the problem
* Prevent inflamed egos
* Respond to truth


### Duplication of Code
* Smell the duplication
* Create libraries of reusable code
* Standardize on design patterns


### Root libraries
* Stylesheet
* HTML Templates
* View rendering
* CRUD patterns
* View Inheritance


### Project #12 - Brain Testing
* Create project plan
    * Requirements.md, Design.md, Code.md, Test.md
    * Set goals and objectives
* Test the team websites
    * Test the site
    * Review the code
    * File defects
* Work on issues


